<div class="container-xxl py-5">
    <div class="container">
        <div class="text-center mx-auto mb-5 wow fadeInUp" data-wow-delay="0.1s" style="max-width: 500px;">
            <div class="d-inline-block rounded-pill bg-secondary text-primary py-1 px-3 mb-3">Community Voices</div>
            <h1 class="display-6 mb-5">Trusted By Tamil Community Members Across Canada</h1>
        </div>
        <div class="owl-carousel testimonial-carousel wow fadeInUp" data-wow-delay="0.1s">
            <div class="testimonial-item text-center">
                <img class="img-fluid bg-light rounded-circle p-2 mx-auto mb-4" src="/img/testimonial-1.jpg" style="width: 100px; height: 100px;">
                <div class="testimonial-text rounded text-center p-4">
                    <p>ATCC has been instrumental in helping me connect with the Tamil community in Toronto. Through their networking events, I found mentors who guided me in my career transition. The organization truly understands the unique challenges we face as immigrants.</p>
                    <h5 class="mb-1">Community Member</h5>
                    <span class="fst-italic">Software Engineer</span>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="testimonial-item text-center">
                <img class="img-fluid bg-light rounded-circle p-2 mx-auto mb-4" src="/img/testimonial-2.jpg" style="width: 100px; height: 100px;">
                <div class="testimonial-text rounded text-center p-4">
                    <p>As a newcomer to Canada, ATCC provided invaluable support in helping me understand the local systems and connect with my cultural roots. Their cultural events and student clubs made me feel at home while pursuing my studies.</p>
                    <h5 class="mb-1">Community Member</h5>
                    <span class="fst-italic">Graduate Student</span>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="testimonial-item text-center">
                <img class="img-fluid bg-light rounded-circle p-2 mx-auto mb-4" src="/img/testimonial-3.jpg" style="width: 100px; height: 100px;">
                <div class="testimonial-text rounded text-center p-4">
                    <p>The business networking opportunities through ATCC have been fantastic. I've been able to showcase my small business to the community and connect with other Tamil entrepreneurs. It's more than just networking - it's building a supportive family.</p>
                    <h5 class="mb-1">Community Member</h5>
                    <span class="fst-italic">Business Owner</span>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
